Usage: specify_pg_keepout [-help] [-bottom <float>] [-left <float>]
                          [-pin <string>] [-right <float>] [-top <float>] {-cell <string> | -inst <string>} {-layer <string> | -layerId <string>}

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-bottom <float>           # specify keepout on the bottom side
                          # (float, optional)
-cell <string>            # specify cell to add PG keepout (string, required)
-inst <string>            # specify inst to add PG keepout (string, required)
-layer <string>           # specify layers to add PG keepout (string, required)
-layerId <string>         # specify layer Ids to add PG keepout
                          # (string, required)
-left <float>             # specify keepout on the left side (float, optional)
-pin <string>             # specify cell to add PG keepout (string, optional)
-right <float>            # specify keepout on the right side (float, optional)
-top <float>              # specify keepout on the top side (float, optional)